= Honey Dill Mustard <R_honey-mustard>

== Ingredients

- 30g (1/4 cup) lemon juice
- 60g (2 tbsp.) honey
- 30g (1.5 tbsp.) Dijon mustard
- 40g (3 tbsp.) olive oil
- 3g (1 tbsp.) dill, minced
- 2g (1/2 tsp.) sugar
- Salt & pepper, to taste

== Steps

Mix all ingredients.

